<paragraph blockId="15.[113,764,994,1274]" pageId="15" pageNumber="170">
<emphasis box="[151,209,994,1017]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="170">Notes</emphasis>
. – 
<taxonomicName box="[245,481,994,1018]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Aspalathus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="15" pageNumber="170" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fascicularis">
<emphasis box="[245,481,994,1018]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="170">Aspalathus fascicularis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was cited by DAHLGREN (1963: 252) as a 
<emphasis box="[302,439,1026,1050]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="170">
nom. 
<taxonomicName box="[360,439,1026,1050]" class="Liliopsida" family="Asparagaceae" genus="Ornithogalum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="15" pageNumber="170" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="dubium">dubium</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
and not treated in his twelve papers published in 
<emphasis box="[326,506,1058,1082]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="170">Botaniska Notiser</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis box="[558,715,1058,1081]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="170">Opera Botanica</emphasis>
[see VAN WYK (1987) for a complete list of Dahlgren’s publications]. The Houttuyn specimen from the 
<collectingRegion box="[565,622,1122,1146]" country="South Africa" name="Western Cape" pageId="15" pageNumber="170">Cape</collectingRegion>
in G-PREL was determined in 1959 by Dahlgren as 
<taxonomicName authority="Lam." authorityName="Lam." box="[550,764,1154,1178]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Aspalathus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="15" pageNumber="170" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="vermiculata">
<emphasis box="[550,701,1154,1178]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="170">A. vermiculata</emphasis>
Lam.
</taxonomicName>
and is designated here as the 
<typeStatus box="[429,528,1186,1210]" pageId="15" pageNumber="170">lectotype</typeStatus>
. 
<taxonomicName box="[538,764,1186,1210]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Aspalathus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="15" pageNumber="170" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fascicularis">
<emphasis box="[538,764,1186,1210]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="170">Aspalathus fascicularis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
should be regarded as the correct name for the taxon often referred to by the later name 
<taxonomicName authority="Lam." authorityName="Lam." box="[423,635,1250,1274]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Aspalathus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="15" pageNumber="170" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="vermiculata">
<emphasis box="[423,572,1250,1274]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="170">A. vermiculata</emphasis>
Lam.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
